## System Overview

本系统是一个基于 **三层架构 + 场景选择器** 的智能开发平台：

- **交互层**: 场景选择器 (`/new-project`, `/feature`, `/bugfix`, `/refactor`, `/design`, `/review`, `/hunt`, `/analyze`, `/loop`, `/simplify`, `/optimize`)
- **能力层**: MemoryService, DesignService, ReviewEngine, TestEngine, OpenDiggerService, NotificationService
- **运行时层**: Claude Code 核心, MCP Servers, archon CLI, 各类工具链

